race.comment: POPULAR MONSTER (7) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 21.68 beating RINGWALD. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Form reads well for this. ASTON ELIJAH (6) hit the frame latest (22.26) when third at this track in a Grade 5. Has already won out of this draw. Makes strong appeal on best. OUCH MY FRANKY (1) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing third beaten 2.75 lengths (22.15). Must be included in calculations. RINGWALD (2) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three at this track and distance most recently.
